James Dunn (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Dunn_(actor) 0 James Howard Dunn (November 2, 1901 – September 1, 1967) was an American actor. He won an Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor for the romantic drama film A Tree Grows in Brooklyn (1946) and received two stars on the Hollywood Walk of Fame in 1960. Early in his career, he was billed as Jimmy Dunn. James_Howard_Dunn ( November_2_,_1901 – September_1_,_1967 ) was an_American_actor .
